The '''Corvair Landspeeder''' was a [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] model produced by [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]]. While on [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]], [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Showolter]] used a Corvair landspeeder that was old by the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].

